<p>We now can go into <strong>/soft/sbin</strong> directory and find new binaries we just installed:</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image"><img src="https://www.unixtutorial.org/images/exfat-binaries-rhel8-1024x377.png" alt="" class="wp-image-3498" srcset="https://34hkt337byg024dljl2cquwz-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/images/exfat-binaries-rhel8-1024x377.png 1024w, https://34hkt337byg024dljl2cquwz-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/images/exfat-binaries-rhel8-300x110.png 300w, https://34hkt337byg024dljl2cquwz-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/images/exfat-binaries-rhel8-768x283.png 768w, https://34hkt337byg024dljl2cquwz-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/images/exfat-binaries-rhel8-270x100.png 270w, https://34hkt337byg024dljl2cquwz-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/images/exfat-binaries-rhel8.png 1370w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure>



